.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, carrot, tomato, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
2. the person eating artichoke is the mexican##1
3. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating carrot##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person eating tomato##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Food         | artichoke | tomato   | carrot | apple  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Sport     | lacrosse        | handball  | parkour    | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, snake, turtle
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, grey, apricot, green
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who likes green is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the person who likes grey is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the snake##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes apricot is between the owner of the horse and the person who likes white##2
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | mouse | horse   | turtle     | snake     |
| Color   | grey  | green | apricot   | white  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, marigold, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, lemonade, mirinda
1. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who growspoppy is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who growstulip##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Flower   | marigold  | poppy      | tulip        | sunflower     |
| Beverage         | lemonade | hot-chocolate | mirinda | almond-milk   |

