.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, mouse, chinchilla
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, march, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | fish   | chinchilla   | mouse | lizard |
| Birthday         | december      | april | may      | march |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

