.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, davidoff, blend
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, tea, milk
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the game-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the blend-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
7. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar    | davidoff   | blend      | game       | prince |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk | tea     | fanta |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

