.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: cherry, plum, grapefruit, apricot
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, whist, snooker
1. the person playing whist is the person eating cherry##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person eating apricot and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person eating apricot is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person eating cherry is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Food   | grapefruit     | plum | apricot   | cherry     |
| Game           | scrabble | backgammon         | snooker         | whist |

