.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, july, november
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, airplane, ship
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the person driving the airplane is the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person driving the ship is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the person driving the bus and the person who's birthday is in may##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday         | april | may      | july       | november    |
| Transport           | quad-bike  | airplane  | ship | bus |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

