.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, poppy, balloon-flower, zinnia
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, german, dutch, british
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the german is on the left of the person who growslily##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the dutch##3
6. the british is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who growslily##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Flower   | poppy         | lily  | balloon-flower     | zinnia         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Nationality      | german         | dutch  | australian   | british |

