.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, water, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca, havana, chaman
 1. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 6. the chaman-smoker is the person drinking water##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking water##2
10. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | water    | soy-milk | hot-chocolate    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Cigar           | havana   | chaman    | pall-mall        | fonseca   |

