.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, writing, skydiving, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, country, dubstep, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of country is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
6. the russian is on the right of the fan of country##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of country##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby      | puzzles                | rock-climbing  | writing | skydiving   |
| Music-Genre           | punk | country | reggae   | dubstep |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

