2. the cottage house is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
4. the cottage house is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who growsorchid is between the person watching western movies and the person who growstulip##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the colonial house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| House          | cottage    | palace  | ranch-style  | colonial |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Flower   | marigold    | orchid     | tulip    | iris |

