.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, punk, trance, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, tulip, marigold
1. the person who growsamaryllis is between the fan of trance and the argentine##2
2. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the fan of blues##1
9. the turkish is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre      | blues | trance      | punk  | reggae    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Flower           | marigold      | tulip       | amaryllis   | orchid      |

