.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, photographer, pilot, architect
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, boat, jet-ski, airplane
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the pilot is in an even position##4
2. the photographer is between the architect and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the architect is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person driving the tram##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | entrepreneur    | pilot | photographer  | architect  |
| Transport   | jet-ski | boat       | airplane | tram |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

