.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, april, july
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, project-manager, police-officer, journalist
1. the project-manager is in an even position##4
2. the project-manager is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is the project-manager##1
7. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the journalist is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Birthday   | july | january      | august | april |
| Job           | police-officer   | project-manager  | social-worker     | journalist |

