3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the fan of pop and the owner of the hamster##2
6. the fan of ambient is the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Pet       | hamster   | chinchilla | lizard | rabbit |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | indie      | pop    | ambient   |

