.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lemon, tomato
City: liverpool, boston, berlin, paris
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, dog, lizard
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the hamster and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| City   | liverpool  | berlin     | paris | boston |
| Pet   | dog   | lizard | guinea-pig | hamster   |

