5. the person who's sport is cycling is the canadian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the french##1
7. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
