.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, lawyer, firefighter, mechanic
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, azure, orange, aquamarine
1. the paramedic is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the firefighter is on the far left##1
5. the lawyer is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who likes orange is on the right of the paramedic##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Job    | firefighter    | lawyer    | paramedic  | mechanic |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| Color     | azure   | amber        | aquamarine   | orange       |

 